  description="Compare international health insurance with direct billing networks. Cashless hospital visits, no upfront payment, and seamless claims for expats."
  headline="Best Expat Insurance with Direct Billing"
  subheadline="Nobody wants to pay $20,000 upfront for hospital care and wait for reimbursement. Here's how to find insurance with direct billing that actually works."
