      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Direct billing availability varies by location, provider, and treatment type. Network coverage should be verified for your specific destination before purchasing. Pre-authorization requirements and timing depend on plan type and procedure. Always confirm network status with both the hospital and insurer before planned treatment.
    </p>
  </div>
